        <div
          class="c27"
        >
          <p
            class="c5 c28"
          >
            Front-end React Developer.
          </p>
          <p
            class="c5 c28"
          >
            Part of the team responsible for migrating the legacy website to a cutting-edge 
            <b
              class="c29"
            >
              Next.JS Typescript
            </b>
             application within an 
            <b
              class="c29"
            >
              NX
            </b>
             monorepo. Instrumental in developing a comprehensive Design System from the ground up using 
            <b
              class="c29"
            >
              Styled Components
            </b>
            . Additionally, involved in creating new applications for clients and internal administration, including an 
            <b
              class="c29"
            >
              EXPO
            </b>
             mobile app for iOS and Android.
          </p>
          <p
            class="c5 c28"
          >
            Proficiently employed 
            <b
              class="c29"
            >
              Jest
            </b>
             and 
            <b
              class="c29"
            >
              MSW
            </b>
             for thorough unit and integration testing, while utilizing 
            <b
              class="c29"
            >
              Cypress
            </b>
             for end-to-end testing.
          </p>
          <p
            class="c5 c28"
          >
            Helped at the implementation of a robust 
            <b
              class="c29"
            >
              CI/CD
            </b>
             pipeline using GitLab for efficient and seamless deployment.
          </p>
