        <div
          class="c27"
        >
          <p
            class="c5 c28"
          >
            Front-end Developer.
          </p>
          <p
            class="c5 c28"
          >
            Contributed to an international project, focusing on web development based on WebComponents, specifically 
            <b
              class="c29"
            >
              LitElement
            </b>
            , and 
            <b
              class="c29"
            >
              Redux
            </b>
            , with seamless communication with REST APIs.
          </p>
          <p
            class="c5 c28"
          >
            Adopted a Test-Driven Development (TDD) approach using 
            <b
              class="c29"
            >
              Karma
            </b>
             with 
            <b
              class="c29"
            >
              Mocha
            </b>
             for comprehensive unit testing.
          </p>
          <p
            class="c5 c28"
          >
            Conducted end-to-end testing using 
            <b
              class="c29"
            >
              Cucumber
            </b>
             and 
            <b
              class="c29"
            >
              WebdriverIO
            </b>
             for thorough functionality testing.
          </p>
          <p
            class="c5 c28"
          >
            Possesses a strong background in pairing code review experience, serving as an approver of the main repository to ensure the validation of merges into the master branch.
          </p>
