        <div
          class="c27"
        >
          <p
            class="c5 c28"
          >
            Front-end Developer.
          </p>
          <p
            class="c5 c28"
          >
            Involved in the development of multiple 
            <b
              class="c29"
            >
              React.JS
            </b>
             web applications, utilizing REST services provided by the Gateway service, primarily based on SAP, Java, or Node.js backend services.
          </p>
          <p
            class="c5 c28"
          >
            Took on the role of a front-end developer lead for an 
            <b
              class="c29"
            >
              Angular JS
            </b>
             application, responsible for onboarding newcomers and overseeing new developments or maintenance. Additionally, proficient in deploying applications across various environments for multiple clients.
          </p>
        </div>
