        <div
          class="c27"
        >
          <p
            class="c5 c28"
          >
            Full Stack Developer.
          </p>
          <p
            class="c5 c28"
          >
            Contributed to the Mobile Development Center, focusing on the main project, an 
            <b
              class="c29"
            >
              IONIC
            </b>
             app with 
            <b
              class="c29"
            >
              Angular JS
            </b>
            . Involved in the development of an instant messaging system using 
            <b
              class="c29"
            >
              Socket.io
            </b>
             and 
            <b
              class="c29"
            >
              Node.js
            </b>
            . Integrated 
            <b
              class="c29"
            >
              Spring Boot
            </b>
             and multiple REST services.
          </p>
          <a
            class="c22 c30 c31"
            data-testid="plain-anchor"
            href="https://www.babelgroup.com/"
            rel="noreferrer"
            target="_blank"
          >
