        </div>
        <div
          class="c27"
        >
          <p
            class="c5 c28"
          >
            Scrum Master and Full Stack Developer.
          </p>
          <p
            class="c5 c28"
          >
            Served as the CTO from November 2016 to April 2017. Acted as the Scrum Master of the main I+D+i project, utilizing 
            <b
              class="c29"
            >
              Java 1.7
            </b>
            , 
            <b
              class="c29"
            >
              Spring 4
            </b>
            , 
            <b
              class="c29"
            >
              GWT 1.7
            </b>
            , 
            <b
              class="c29"
            >
              Hibernate 5
            </b>
            , and 
            <b
              class="c29"
            >
              MySQL 5.6
            </b>
            . Implemented 
            <b
              class="c29"
            >
              IONIC 2
            </b>
             and 
            <b
              class="c29"
            >
              Angular
            </b>
             for mobile development.
          </p>
          <p
            class="c5 c28"
          >
            Implemented an 
            <b
              class="c29"
            >
              Arduino
            </b>
             monitoring system for real-time information within the application.
          </p>
          <p
            class="c5 c28"
          >
            Demonstrated proficiency in utilizing 
            <b
              class="c29"
            >
              Maven
            </b>
            , 
            <b
              class="c29"
            >
              Sonarqube
            </b>
            , and 
            <b
              class="c29"
            >
              JUnit
            </b>
            , along with 
            <b
              class="c29"
            >
              Mockito
            </b>
             for testing and validating clean code.
          </p>
          <p
            class="c5 c28"
          >
            Involved in front-end development for various customers, employing 
            <b
              class="c29"
            >
              CSS3
            </b>
            , 
            <b
              class="c29"
            >
              jQuery
            </b>
            , and 
            <b
              class="c29"
            >
              HTML5
            </b>
            .
          </p>
          <p
            class="c5 c28"
          >
            Worked as a 
            <b
              class="c29"
            >
              Java
            </b>
             consultant, focusing on back-end developments in PSA Peugeot-Citroën. Involved in incident resolution and new functionalities development, utilizing 
            <b
              class="c29"
            >
              Spring 3 MVC
            </b>
            , 
            <b
              class="c29"
            >
              Hibernate
            </b>
            , 
            <b
              class="c29"
            >
              Struts 2
            </b>
             and DB 
            <b
              class="c29"
            >
              Oracle
            </b>
            .
          </p>
          <a
            class="c22 c30 c31"
            data-testid="plain-anchor"
            href="https://ioon.es/"
            rel="noreferrer"
            target="_blank"
          >
