            class="c5 c28"
          >
            Full Stack Developer.
          </p>
          <p
            class="c5 c28"
          >
            Involved in back-end development using 
            <b
              class="c29"
            >
              Perl
            </b>
             and the Catalyst Framework, alongside various CPAN modules for seamless database integration, including 
            <b
              class="c29"
            >
              Oracle
            </b>
             and 
            <b
              class="c29"
            >
              MongoDB
            </b>
            .
          </p>
          <p
            class="c5 c28"
          >
            Utilized the 
            <b
              class="c29"
            >
              ExtJS
            </b>
             Framework for front-end development.
          </p>
          <p
            class="c5 c28"
          >
            Integrated SOAP webservices for streamlined communication.
          </p>
